  <brief_title>Phase IV Clinical Trial to Investigate the Effect on Blood Glucose of Evogliptin in Patients With Type 2 Diabetes</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, Randomized, Double-blind, Active-contrelled, Parallel-group, Phase IV Clinical Trial to Investigate the Effect on Blood Glucose of Evogliptin After Oral Administration in Patiend With Type 2 Diabetes</official_title>
